Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since when was it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are itsukarada?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Being honest became whining{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honne ga yowane ni nattana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Standing firm became strength{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nigenai koto ga tsuyosa ni natta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have you found it yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa mitsukaranai?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not confidence, your true self{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jishin janaku jibun jishin{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There must be something\NI've forgotten that I still haven't found{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kitto mada sagasetenai wasuremono ga aruhazu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Words I want to say\NThat I still haven't said{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}zutto mada tsutaetenai tsutaetai kotoba{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you would watch me, I'd captivate you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mitete kurerunara misete miserunoni{\i0}
