Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ga boku wo aishinuku koto{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it alright to still believe in that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa mada shinjitemo iika?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I smolder because I've actually burned{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kusuburuno wa chanto moeta karada{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter where this journey takes us{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doko e mukau tabi datoshitemo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll just open my eyes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada me wo mihiraite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.87,0:01:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And dream my dream{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.87,0:01:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yume wo miru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And know my dream{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yume wo shiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,THE TEAM BATTLE BEGINS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nova!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it was a good lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a lesson to take with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world,\Nthere's always someone stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nova!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,At least die gloriously, you loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were right about one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's always someone stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam! Big Guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rushing while carrying three was rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Crocodine!\N-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a little more gentle, Big Guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! But be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So all the Disciples of Aban are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose we can't back down anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Look Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I impaled his head and he still lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They really are just like Flazzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They're metallic lifeforms\Nmade by Forbidden Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If we find their cores and use\Nour Air technique, they can be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. We just need\Nto find their cores!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother searching!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Our cores are right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The same as you humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:04:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he an idiot?!\NHe just revealed their weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing that won't help you beat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you humans,\Nit's meaningless if you can't hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This makes it five against five.\NWe're evenly matched.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As a reward for impaling me,\Nlet us show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.09,0:04:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the true power of the Hadorra Royal Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Their confidence is almost terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,After all we've been through,\Nour teamwork won't lose to those puppets!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, try to take care of that horse-head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Without his spell reflector,\NI can blow them all away
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,with my Extreme Spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take the big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, which one is their leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra isn't here, so that queen\Nshould be their leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:04:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be taking the armoured one, Albinass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You will not, Hym.\NYou must take the Hero, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're telling me\Nto just ignore what he did to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be happy\Nuntil I impale his head, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We are all pieces for Lord Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We live and die all for Lord Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I can't argue with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to fight, revealing their\Nstrengths will better serve Lord Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to know when to switch gears!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it, Hym. Keep it up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you my opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How confident. You could have\Npierced my core from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No need for concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I am merely a piece\Nbearing the role of queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A piece has no gender.\NNo need to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think you underestimate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That one must be a pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think pitting the weakest piece\Nagainst Dai would actually stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one underestimating us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but I believe you're unfamiliar\Nwith the game of chess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In chess, there are no stronger\Nor weaker pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only a difference in abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A pawn is not necessarily\Nweaker than a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all in how you use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Recognize your opponent's abilities\Nand deploy your pieces accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the basic strategy in chess\Nto stop your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can hit the heart with Air Slash...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban Style Sword Technique! {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Air Slash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're using this knife against me,\Nyou still don't understand my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is that thing on your back\Njust a decoration?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym is unmatched\Nin close-quarters combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Without your Hero, it seems\Nyou're the ones at a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't shatter that shield.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to stop his movements!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,For a human to attain such speed\Nis quite a feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The speed...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,no one can eclipse my agility and speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I appears that our piece placement\Nwas better than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I merely need to take out\Nthe queen who commands them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It hardly bears mentioning,\Nbut I, too, am very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!\NThey're controlling the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I need them grouped together,\Notherwise I can't cast my spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.07,0:10:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What can we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And where did that pointy guy\Nwho was chasing me go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wide open!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My brand-new staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 80% of my body is blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't suggest touching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back! Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! You don't have time\Nto be worried about others!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It won't come out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What a disappointment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't carry around a weapon\Nthat you can't even use!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that he hasn't yet\Nmastered that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that we need not bother\Nsummoning Lord Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so sure about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible! He actually hit me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, we humans aren't pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think you can\Napproach this like a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Gira!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Futile, futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Draw it. This is your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At this rate, everyone is going to die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I could draw my sword,\NI could defeat them easily!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darn it! Why won't it come out?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What a joke. You really can't draw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not worth Lord Hadorra's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My Heat Knuckle can easily shatter\Nsomeone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to finish things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll take your head\Nbefore you feel any pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nova?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, you feeble weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick! Give me your staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nova!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving me, Nova!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Hero's duty to protect the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. He's just unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He exhausted himself\Nby using up the last of his Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He fought to the very limit.\NHe's tougher than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To the very limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}REFRACTOR FIST{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}TOMAKUGUTSOSHO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All this training and I couldn't\Ndraw my sword once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel's already mastered\Nthe Dark Armour Spear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it, Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural.\NOf course you can't draw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sword of Dai can't be unsheathed\Nto face a retired warrior like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a reason that\Nyou can't draw your sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,it's in your inability\Nto properly read your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The issue is in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever since I sliced that giant\NSovereign Rock Castle,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been unconsciously\Nrelying on the sword's power!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mistook the power I wielded\Nwith the sword as my own!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}my sword has its own soul.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can read my enemies\Nfar better than I can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd forgotten that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only when I've fought to the limit\Nwith my own strength,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will my sword lend its power to me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nova, seeing you fight so desperately{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}has made me understand\Nwhat Ron Berku tried to teach me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess we both have\Na lot to learn as Heroes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If I still can't draw my sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it means there's still a way\Nto defeat them without it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You and your meddling!\NYou'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Full power {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Dragonic Aura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, knock Hym this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right! I'm not the only one\Nwho can use Air attacks!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban Style Spear Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Air Strike!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! That's one down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You still haven't mastered Air Strike?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that it's not an easy skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But the queen spit this out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,shifting my aim from Hym's core.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Without this, I could have ended it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's instantly fatal\Ndepending on where you're hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd suggest healing it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, we need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone gather for a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Kiari!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. I can't lift my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Fenbren.\N-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes things easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I misjudged them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Albinass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I did, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Disciples of Aban have grown far more\Npowerful than what Lord Hadorra described.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Our abilities surpass theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But their experience\Nmakes them relentless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't be underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be okay, Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym is going to fight without an arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do they get that tenacity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp has a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Their solidarity and sense of purpose\Nare terrifyingly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But Dai, while I missed,\Nyou were on the right track.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to do everything yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I made my own discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Individually, their abilities\Nare far beyond our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't win fighting power\Nwith power or speed with speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We should fight their strengths\Nwith different strengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.\NMatching their strengths is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's switch things up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, confuse the big one with your speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And Big Guy, use your strength\Nto overpower the knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai and Hyunckel, I need you to take\Nthe other three at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep together as a team!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to prepare my Medoroa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the knight's mirror is disabled,\Ntry to gather them together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be firing a huge spell,\Nso get some distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Beast King Redemption Blast!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't beat me\Nwith an Aura Flow this weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about the other whirlpool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I risked my life\Nin the Baruji Whirlpool for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My new attack will tear you apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A second twister with a reverse spin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Beast King Indomitable Blast!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sigma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Everybody scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A spell won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Medoroa!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}W-What power!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's worth bragging about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well done learning such a spell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's amazing, Popp!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what all that training was for!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely hit them this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,One good hit with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:21:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and we win!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those trivial little memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honno sasaina omoidetachi ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:22:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're still in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:22:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}itsumade tattemo kono mune wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As embers that keep me burning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kogashi tsuzukeru tomoshibi ni naru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single transparent beam of light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitosuji no toumei na hikari ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.59,0:23:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lights the way before me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.59,0:23:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}me no mae wo terashite yuku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is little that I can do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ni dekiru koto wa ikutsu mo naisa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.43,0:23:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just keep on to the future\NI managed to grasp through my faith{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.43,0:23:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shinjinuita saki ni te ni shita mirai wo\Nsusunde yuke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.07,0:23:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fierce team battle was ended\Nby Popp's new spell, Medoroa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Chiu infiltrates\Nthe Field of Death with his companions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.29,0:23:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They get closer to the secret\Nof the Dark Army's stronghold.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.88,0:23:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the hand of the Dark Army\Nreaches towards them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.51,0:23:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"We're the Beast King Commandos"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.35,0:23:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.56,0:23:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,
